OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FGenerally sunny and very warm
OL,6,For hot inland, but breezier than
OL,7,Frecently, especially along the coast
OL,8,Fwhere low cloud may linger through the
OL,9,Fday in places. Temperatures will be
OL,10,Fslightly cooler than in recent days,
OL,11,Fespecially along coastal areas.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAnother exceptionally warm
OL,14,Fnight, especially in large towns and
OL,15,Fcities, with humid conditions
OL,16,Fpersisting. Some largely clear skies
OL,17,Fbut a chance of showers or thundery
OL,18,Foutbreaks around dawn on Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
