OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FOutbreaks of rain soon
OL,6,Fclearing into the North Sea leading to
OL,7,Fanother hot or exceptionally hot day.
OL,8,FSunny spells and a few showers
OL,9,Fotherwise, mostly in the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStill
OL,12,Fvery warm or hot Saturday, with a
OL,13,Fchance of showers or thunderstorms.
OL,14,FBreezy with outbreaks of rain pushing
OL,15,Feast on Sunday, cooler. Sunny spells
OL,16,Fand isolated showers on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
